rules.description: HHKB Arrow Mode (fn + semicolon/slash/open_bracket/quote to arrow keys, etc)
HHKB Media Key Mode (fn + asdf to Volume down/up/mute, eject)
HHKB Media Key Mode Extension (fn + zxc to playpause/prev/next)
left control + left shift + ` (backtick) - launches a new iTerm2 window with the default profile

to.shell_command: osascript -e 'tell app "iTerm2"' -e 'create window with default profile' -e activate -e end

rules.description: HHKB Scroll Mode (fn + K/L/,/. to home/end/pgup/pgdown)
